request.description:
Get a **list** of all the registered rebels, where a rebel has the following, simplified schema:

``` json
{
  "id": 1,
  "name": "John Smith",
  "age": 30,
  "gender": "MALE",
  "location": {
    "name": "Venus",
    "latitude": 50,
    "longitude": 57
  },
  "inventory": {
    "weapons": 1,
    "ammo": 2,
    "water": 3,
    "food": 4
  }
}

```

Post a new rebel. Request body must respect the example presented below, where:

*   `"gender"` must be either "`MALE"`, `"FEMALE"` or `"OTHER"`;
*   `"latitude"` and `"longitude"` must be an integer number between 0 and 90 degrees;


and the other fields are self explanatory.
